; menudata.a65 - Menu entry tables and key-value tables (64tass port)
;
; Menu entry structure (23 bytes per entry):
;   1 byte   entry type
;   3 bytes  long pointer to menu entry text
;   3 bytes  long pointer to routine / submenu / preset table
;   1 byte   data type of parameter (OPTTYPE_*)
;   3 bytes  long pointer to parameter value
;   3 bytes  long pointer to text description
;   3 bytes  long pointer to change-hook function (addr-1)
;   3 bytes  long pointer to post-hook function (addr-1)
;   3 bytes  long pointer to isEnabled function (addr-1)


